 there are other factors involved.  What are they?  Super twink?  First to zone when there's trouble?  I'm not acuuuusssing you of anything, just wondering.<br><br>Love,<br>Mulamen.</p><br /><span class="sm">----------------------------</span><br /><a href="HTTP://www.guildportal.com/Guild.aspx?GuildID=15391&TabID=129880" target="akztarg"> Aude Sapere </a></td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform2"><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%"><tr><td id="fs8">Posting from A Flying Dog</td></tr></table>
