ariety of roles that people expect zerkers to be &quot;top notch&quot; in. Until SOE gives us a clear class definition for them, we won't know that though. Some people expected them to be the next ranger, with awesome ranged DPS. Others expected them to be a true offtank, and others expected them to provide almost rogueish DPS with rangerish utility. They can't be them all, and yet, at the moment, they're none. That makes them an underdefined class, at least for the moment. <br><br><i><span class="sm">Edited, Tue Mar 22 13:17:19 2005 by Jiggidyjay</span class="sm"></i></p><br /><span class="sm">----------------------------</span><br /><a href="HTTP://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=1006062" target="akztarg">Jiggidyjay</a> - <span class="sm">Mr Ranger</span class="sm"><br><a href="HTTP://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=1003866" target="akztarg">Zingin Ansinging</a> - <span class="sm">Mr Bard of <a href="HTTP://firestormers.com/viewnews.php" target="akztarg">The Firestormers</a></span class="sm"><br><a href="HTTP://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=1006061" target="akztarg">Zolotaya</a> - <span class="sm">Ms Necro</span class="sm"><br><a href="HTTP://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=1189723" target="akztarg">Zeibis</a> - <span class="sm">Mr Monk</span class="sm"></td></td></tr><tr><td colspan="2" class="mform2"><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" width="100%"><tr><td id="fs8">Posting from the Oval Office.</td></tr></table>
